WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:01.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Mei grunts]
-[shatters]</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:01.840 --> 00:00:03.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was so heavy.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:04.130 --> 00:00:06.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, man, when I'm around
sheltered girls,</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:06.720 --> 00:00:09.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't help but let that bully
in me rear its ugly head.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:10.010 --> 00:00:11.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here I am,</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:11.090 --> 00:00:13.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>born in a world
filled with gun smoke,</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:13.310 --> 00:00:15.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>barely surviving
by drinking muddy water,</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:15.520 --> 00:00:17.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>risking my life
on the battlefield.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:18.390 --> 00:00:20.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But not them, oh, no, no, no.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:21.480 --> 00:00:23.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire
persecuted witches?</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:24.270 --> 00:00:25.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wrong.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:25.610 --> 00:00:28.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's the witches who look down
on the rest of society!</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:29.780 --> 00:00:31.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Those arrogant snots
piss me off!</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:32.410 --> 00:00:35.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[glass scraping, clinking]</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:36.830 --> 00:00:39.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Kissing groans]</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:41.750 --> 00:00:44.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shuddered breathing]</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:44.880 --> 00:00:47.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MEI]
What a pleasant surprise!</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:47.550 --> 00:00:48.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Kissing groans]
-My orders were</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:48.880 --> 00:00:50.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to bring you back with a pulse.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:50.970 --> 00:00:52.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm glad you made it,
little girl.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:53.050 --> 00:00:54.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For the most part.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:55.100 --> 00:00:56.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KISSING]
It, it hurts.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:57.060 --> 00:00:58.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My head. Is that...</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:59.430 --> 00:01:00.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>blood?</b></Default>

c0000024
00:01:02.600 --> 00:01:03.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aah!</b></Default>

c0000025
00:01:04.060 --> 00:01:06.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've been wondering
where your astral crest was.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:01:06.610 --> 00:01:09.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Turns out it's been hiding
in your eyes this whole time!</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:09.570 --> 00:01:10.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mei chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:11.410 --> 00:01:12.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KISSING]
Uncle On.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:12.990 --> 00:01:14.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now I understand
what you meant.</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:15.450 --> 00:01:17.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing good can come from war.</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:18.160 --> 00:01:19.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How can anything positive</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:19.660 --> 00:01:22.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>come from something
that hurts so much?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:22.290 --> 00:01:23.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's that?</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:23.540 --> 00:01:25.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you having
a change of heart?</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:26.000 --> 00:01:27.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:27.340 --> 00:01:29.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's put an end to this war</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:29.670 --> 00:01:32.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by completely annihilating
the Imperial army!</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:32.840 --> 00:01:35.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll to show you mercy
with a quick death.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:35.260 --> 00:01:36.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're gonna show me mercy?</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:37.430 --> 00:01:39.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't get too cocky,
little girl.</b></Default>

c0000041
00:01:41.230 --> 00:01:42.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You survived one blow.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:01:43.100 --> 00:01:44.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The next time
you hear a gunshot,</b></Default>

c0000043
00:01:44.650 --> 00:01:46.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this whole war'll be over.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:01:46.820 --> 00:01:49.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, this war will be over
for all of you.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:01:50.190 --> 00:01:51.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000046
00:01:52.030 --> 00:01:58.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000047
00:01:58.790 --> 00:02:00.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON] [groaning]
What?</b></Default>

c0000048
00:02:00.120 --> 00:02:01.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>LAST CRUSADE:
THE UNFORGIVEN ONE</b></Default>

c0000049
00:02:02.120 --> 00:02:03.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000050
00:02:04.120 --> 00:02:06.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Aw, that's too bad!</b></Default>

c0000051
00:02:06.500 --> 00:02:08.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If only I had pulled on this
just a moment sooner,</b></Default>

c0000052
00:02:09.210 --> 00:02:11.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would've popped
your big head clean off!</b></Default>

c0000053
00:02:12.130 --> 00:02:13.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, well,</b></Default>

c0000054
00:02:13.380 --> 00:02:15.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just not used to glasses.</b></Default>

c0000055
00:02:16.180 --> 00:02:17.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
Imperial drones.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:02:17.890 --> 00:02:19.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You always vex me.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You call us witches and demons</b></Default>

c0000058
00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:22.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with disdain on your tongue.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:02:22.810 --> 00:02:25.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yet you, yourself,
use astral spirits.</b></Default>

c0000060
00:02:25.810 --> 00:02:26.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Whoa, hey.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:02:27.020 --> 00:02:28.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're venting
your frustrations</b></Default>

c0000062
00:02:28.270 --> 00:02:29.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the wrong person.</b></Default>

c0000063
00:02:29.530 --> 00:02:30.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
Hm?</b></Default>

c0000064
00:02:30.610 --> 00:02:32.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, come on, just think.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:02:32.490 --> 00:02:33.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Without your
royal family's help,</b></Default>

c0000066
00:02:34.030 --> 00:02:36.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we wouldn't be using
astral powers, would we?</b></Default>

c0000067
00:02:37.240 --> 00:02:38.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We knew there was a traitor</b></Default>

c0000068
00:02:38.700 --> 00:02:40.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>lurking in the royal family.</b></Default>

c0000069
00:02:41.160 --> 00:02:43.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm a great listener
if you'd like to talk it out.</b></Default>

c0000070
00:02:43.750 --> 00:02:45.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
Ugh, you're just being obtuse.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:02:46.040 --> 00:02:48.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Look, I'll tell you who it is
if you can beat me.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:02:48.460 --> 00:02:50.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do I really need
to spell it out or what?</b></Default>

c0000073
00:02:50.670 --> 00:02:52.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're making me sound
cheesy right now.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:02:52.510 --> 00:02:54.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah. My apologies.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:02:54.720 --> 00:02:55.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That wasn't like me.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:02:57.260 --> 00:02:59.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA] Fourth generation
of the planet Thread.</b></Default>

c0000077
00:03:00.010 --> 00:03:01.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This doesn't exist
in the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:03:02.220 --> 00:03:05.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's a new type that was born
within the Empire's vortex.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:09.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I bet you want all the secrets
locked away in my head.</b></Default>

c0000080
00:03:10.190 --> 00:03:11.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not going anywhere.</b></Default>

c0000081
00:03:11.980 --> 00:03:14.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not when you are this close
to forbidden knowledge.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:03:14.820 --> 00:03:17.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With a beautiful lady
beckoning me to stay,</b></Default>

c0000083
00:03:17.820 --> 00:03:19.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>walking away
would be ungentlemanly.</b></Default>

c0000084
00:03:20.160 --> 00:03:21.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
If I'm being perfectly honest,</b></Default>

c0000085
00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:23.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't hate your theatrics.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:03:23.620 --> 00:03:24.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're charming.</b></Default>

c0000087
00:03:24.660 --> 00:03:26.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I'd like to take a peek
behind the curtain</b></Default>

c0000088
00:03:26.500 --> 00:03:27.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and see your real face.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:03:28.290 --> 00:03:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can wear a mask
all you want,</b></Default>

c0000090
00:03:30.090 --> 00:03:32.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but you can't hide your ugly,
cruel nature.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:03:32.250 --> 00:03:34.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's there.
Very demon-like.</b></Default>

c0000092
00:03:34.170 --> 00:03:36.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Really?
Whatever do you mean?</b></Default>

c0000093
00:03:36.300 --> 00:03:39.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Show's over! I'll drag you
off stage by force if I must!</b></Default>

c0000094
00:03:41.720 --> 00:03:44.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lovely, who doesn't love
a good curtain call?</b></Default>

c0000095
00:03:44.430 --> 00:03:49.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000096
00:03:49.560 --> 00:03:50.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
Really?</b></Default>

c0000097
00:03:50.770 --> 00:03:52.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] Though it won't take
any physical damage</b></Default>

c0000098
00:03:52.900 --> 00:03:53.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from your attacks,</b></Default>

c0000099
00:03:53.940 --> 00:03:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it can still interact
with objects in this world.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:03:56.700 --> 00:03:57.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
Sounds like you're bragging</b></Default>

c0000101
00:03:57.950 --> 00:03:59.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>about your invincibility.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:03:59.530 --> 00:04:02.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] Oh,
that's exactly what I'm doing.</b></Default>

c0000103
00:04:02.490 --> 00:04:04.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the astral spirit
of sin!</b></Default>

c0000104
00:04:04.870 --> 00:04:05.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[scoffs]</b></Default>

c0000105
00:04:07.160 --> 00:04:08.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Growley grunts]</b></Default>

c0000106
00:04:08.710 --> 00:04:10.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

c0000107
00:04:11.670 --> 00:04:14.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS] If I eliminate you,
wouldn't my sin also disappear?</b></Default>

c0000108
00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:17.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
On the contrary.</b></Default>

c0000109
00:04:17.880 --> 00:04:20.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your sin would
multiply endlessly.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:04:22.220 --> 00:04:23.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[NAMELESS] Take it.
-[arm clangs]</b></Default>

c0000111
00:04:23.850 --> 00:04:24.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
You gave up your arm.</b></Default>

c0000112
00:04:26.100 --> 00:04:27.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
It's a prosthetic anyway.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:04:28.100 --> 00:04:30.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thumps]
-[NAMELESS] Again?</b></Default>

c0000114
00:04:31.020 --> 00:04:33.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] Your "second offense"
is even more grievous</b></Default>

c0000115
00:04:33.730 --> 00:04:36.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>than your first
pitiful miscalculation.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:04:36.740 --> 00:04:38.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your sin will swallow
you whole.</b></Default>

c0000117
00:04:39.070 --> 00:04:44.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000118
00:04:44.700 --> 00:04:45.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thumps]</b></Default>

c0000119
00:04:45.830 --> 00:04:48.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
Anti-astral grenade, huh?</b></Default>

c0000120
00:04:48.910 --> 00:04:51.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS] It may not take
physical damage,</b></Default>

c0000121
00:04:51.290 --> 00:04:54.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but the spirit itself can
receive astral damage, right?</b></Default>

c0000122
00:04:55.630 --> 00:04:58.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen
your astral spirit now.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:04:58.090 --> 00:05:00.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next time, I'll vanquish it.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:05:01.130 --> 00:05:03.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY] Do you think
I'll let you get away?</b></Default>

c0000125
00:05:04.010 --> 00:05:10.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000126
00:05:11.810 --> 00:05:14.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[coughing, groaning]</b></Default>

c0000127
00:05:14.940 --> 00:05:16.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
Imperial scum.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:17.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Curse you and your grenade!</b></Default>

c0000129
00:05:18.070 --> 00:05:21.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000130
00:05:22.320 --> 00:05:23.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GROWLEY]
But you won't get far.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:05:24.240 --> 00:05:26.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The astral spirit of sin
is in motion.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:05:26.950 --> 00:05:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Inescapable and dogged
in its pursuit.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:05:30.250 --> 00:05:33.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It will follow you to the ends
of this nation and beyond!</b></Default>

c0000134
00:05:33.710 --> 00:05:36.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mismis panting]</b></Default>

c0000135
00:05:37.550 --> 00:05:39.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts, groans]</b></Default>

c0000136
00:05:39.630 --> 00:05:41.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't step on the snow,
you hear me?</b></Default>

c0000137
00:05:41.760 --> 00:05:43.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why? Jhin,
is everything all right?</b></Default>

c0000138
00:05:44.680 --> 00:05:46.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not in pain right now?</b></Default>

c0000139
00:05:46.510 --> 00:05:48.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. Why would I be in any pain?</b></Default>

c0000140
00:05:48.770 --> 00:05:50.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Sisbell gasps]
-[JHIN] It's the snow.</b></Default>

c0000141
00:05:50.680 --> 00:05:51.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feels like it bit me.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:05:51.980 --> 00:05:53.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[all gasp]
-The path.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:05:53.900 --> 00:05:56.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we go this way, it'll be
like walking through needles!</b></Default>

c0000144
00:05:57.110 --> 00:05:58.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you think
I'm the only one</b></Default>

c0000145
00:05:58.530 --> 00:05:59.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>being attacked by the snow?</b></Default>

c0000146
00:06:00.110 --> 00:06:01.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000147
00:06:01.990 --> 00:06:03.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know.</b></Default>

c0000148
00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:06.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts] Some things
created by astral art</b></Default>

c0000149
00:06:06.700 --> 00:06:07.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>can react a certain way</b></Default>

c0000150
00:06:07.830 --> 00:06:10.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>depending on whether
one has astral energy or not.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:06:10.540 --> 00:06:12.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just like
the doors and gadgets</b></Default>

c0000152
00:06:12.330 --> 00:06:13.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the royal palace!</b></Default>

c0000153
00:06:13.920 --> 00:06:16.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh! Disregard
what I just said, please.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:06:16.340 --> 00:06:17.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elaborate.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:19.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This snow,
it will attack anyone</b></Default>

c0000156
00:06:20.050 --> 00:06:21.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who doesn't have
an astral crest on them!</b></Default>

c0000157
00:06:22.420 --> 00:06:23.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, boss. you're up.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:06:24.180 --> 00:06:25.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
I knew you'd say that!</b></Default>

c0000159
00:06:26.350 --> 00:06:28.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You work your captain
way too hard!</b></Default>

c0000160
00:06:28.350 --> 00:06:30.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're lucky.
I'm such a nice boss!</b></Default>

c0000161
00:06:30.390 --> 00:06:31.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
You're doing great, boss.</b></Default>

c0000162
00:06:31.980 --> 00:06:33.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Keep kicking the snow away.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:06:33.980 --> 00:06:36.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now then.
Light 'em up.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:06:36.190 --> 00:06:38.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gunshots]</b></Default>

c0000165
00:06:38.570 --> 00:06:41.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000166
00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:46.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Jhin grunts]
-Good shot, Jhin!</b></Default>

c0000167
00:06:46.110 --> 00:06:47.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
This way, you guys!</b></Default>

c0000168
00:06:47.660 --> 00:06:49.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's one room way
in the back that's empty!</b></Default>

c0000169
00:06:50.490 --> 00:06:53.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] Nene. Walk exactly
where the boss has walked.</b></Default>

c0000170
00:06:53.290 --> 00:06:54.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't touch the snow,
or else!</b></Default>

c0000171
00:06:54.960 --> 00:06:57.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE] [panting]
Got it!</b></Default>

c0000172
00:06:57.210 --> 00:06:58.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-[door thuds]</b></Default>

c0000173
00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:00.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000174
00:07:01.460 --> 00:07:03.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's one persistent old lady.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:07:03.760 --> 00:07:06.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL] You can run,
but you can't hide!</b></Default>

c0000176
00:07:06.220 --> 00:07:09.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You may be faster than me,
but you're in my world.</b></Default>

c0000177
00:07:09.350 --> 00:07:11.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And every step you take
is pressed into the snow</b></Default>

c0000178
00:07:11.810 --> 00:07:13.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>like a map
that leads me to you!</b></Default>

c0000179
00:07:14.350 --> 00:07:15.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Sisbell gasps]
-Stay quiet!</b></Default>

c0000180
00:07:16.190 --> 00:07:19.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL] [chuckles]
Do it.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:07:20.320 --> 00:07:22.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thuds]
-[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000182
00:07:22.530 --> 00:07:24.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL]
Crush the Imperial soldiers.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:07:24.820 --> 00:07:26.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only Lady Sisbell shall...</b></Default>

c0000184
00:07:27.360 --> 00:07:29.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She shall...
What?</b></Default>

c0000185
00:07:29.780 --> 00:07:33.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000186
00:07:33.500 --> 00:07:35.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL]
Where is she?</b></Default>

c0000187
00:07:35.620 --> 00:07:37.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
Right behind ya, you old hag.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:40.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We weren't hiding in
the last room like you thought.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:07:41.170 --> 00:07:43.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We were in the room
just before it.</b></Default>

c0000190
00:07:43.090 --> 00:07:45.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS] There's one room
way in the back that's empty!</b></Default>

c0000191
00:07:46.760 --> 00:07:49.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL] But you lot left
an entire trail of footprints!</b></Default>

c0000192
00:07:49.970 --> 00:07:51.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, but then we backtracked.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:07:51.970 --> 00:07:54.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After we made footprints
that led all the way</b></Default>

c0000194
00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:55.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the back room,</b></Default>

c0000195
00:07:55.390 --> 00:07:56.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we stopped there
and turned around,</b></Default>

c0000196
00:07:57.060 --> 00:07:59.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then walked on top
of our own tracks.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:08:00.230 --> 00:08:02.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[GRUGELL] Sneaky rats,
damn Imperial soldie--</b></Default>

c0000198
00:08:03.110 --> 00:08:05.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Grugell groans]
-Underestimate our captain</b></Default>

c0000199
00:08:05.110 --> 00:08:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and you pay the price.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:08:08.910 --> 00:08:10.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wow, your plan worked so well.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:08:11.530 --> 00:08:12.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Does this mean we're safe now?</b></Default>

c0000202
00:08:13.370 --> 00:08:14.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000203
00:08:15.330 --> 00:08:17.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] This isn't the time
to feel safe.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:08:17.210 --> 00:08:19.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to head
downstairs, fast!</b></Default>

c0000205
00:08:19.630 --> 00:08:20.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000206
00:08:21.000 --> 00:08:23.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now then...if you'll excuse me,
good sir.</b></Default>

c0000207
00:08:24.090 --> 00:08:25.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
You're leaving?</b></Default>

c0000208
00:08:25.420 --> 00:08:28.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes. The Imperial army
is attacking the palace.</b></Default>

c0000209
00:08:28.840 --> 00:08:31.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The head of house should
make an appearance, right?</b></Default>

c0000210
00:08:31.890 --> 00:08:33.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I commend you
for your performance.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:08:33.720 --> 00:08:35.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hats off to you, bravo!</b></Default>

c0000212
00:08:35.680 --> 00:08:37.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But...it seems</b></Default>

c0000213
00:08:37.350 --> 00:08:39.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we were able
to complete our mission!</b></Default>

c0000214
00:08:39.850 --> 00:08:41.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
What does he mean by that?</b></Default>

c0000215
00:08:41.520 --> 00:08:43.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Has he already gotten
his hands on Sisbell?</b></Default>

c0000216
00:08:44.190 --> 00:08:45.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or could he be bluffing?</b></Default>

c0000217
00:08:46.440 --> 00:08:47.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think I'll let you leave?</b></Default>

c0000218
00:08:48.490 --> 00:08:49.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Talisman laughs]</b></Default>

c0000219
00:08:50.820 --> 00:08:53.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[ISKA] What the hell?
[TALISMAN] Good instincts.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:08:53.450 --> 00:08:54.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've got your guard up
after sensing</b></Default>

c0000221
00:08:55.080 --> 00:08:56.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the movement beneath you
is not the same</b></Default>

c0000222
00:08:56.910 --> 00:08:58.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as my wave astral art.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:08:58.750 --> 00:09:00.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, those instincts
were right,</b></Default>

c0000224
00:09:00.750 --> 00:09:02.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this isn't my astral art.</b></Default>

c0000225
00:09:02.840 --> 00:09:04.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] This phenomenon.
What is it?</b></Default>

c0000226
00:09:05.500 --> 00:09:06.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've seen it before.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:09:07.340 --> 00:09:08.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mere moments ago,</b></Default>

c0000228
00:09:09.720 --> 00:09:13.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I spoke to a witch who escaped
from prison some time ago.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:09:14.260 --> 00:09:15.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
A witch?</b></Default>

c0000230
00:09:15.510 --> 00:09:17.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A lady you are
quite familiar with.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:09:17.850 --> 00:09:18.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Hang on.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:09:19.690 --> 00:09:20.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TALISMAN]
You got us once before,</b></Default>

c0000233
00:09:21.060 --> 00:09:22.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll give you that.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:09:22.230 --> 00:09:24.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it was a massive error
in judgment</b></Default>

c0000235
00:09:24.150 --> 00:09:26.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to think an inquisition
quarantine room</b></Default>

c0000236
00:09:26.110 --> 00:09:27.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could contain her.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:09:27.820 --> 00:09:30.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all,
she isn't human anymore.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:09:31.070 --> 00:09:33.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's blossomed
into a true witch.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:09:34.370 --> 00:09:35.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Attraction force?</b></Default>

c0000240
00:09:36.160 --> 00:09:39.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Witch? Gravity?
Could it be...?</b></Default>

c0000241
00:09:39.500 --> 00:09:40.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Farewell, friend.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:09:41.210 --> 00:09:42.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Loving Saint Disciple.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:09:44.330 --> 00:09:45.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey!</b></Default>

c0000244
00:09:46.250 --> 00:09:47.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:09:48.670 --> 00:09:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE]
Super Cannon.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:52.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Corpse Magic Bullet.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:09:55.180 --> 00:09:56.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Mismis groaning]</b></Default>

c0000248
00:09:57.850 --> 00:09:59.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000249
00:10:00.730 --> 00:10:01.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000250
00:10:03.480 --> 00:10:04.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What happened?</b></Default>

c0000251
00:10:06.360 --> 00:10:08.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The entire room is blown apart.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:10:08.980 --> 00:10:10.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[JHIN] Hey, boss.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000253
00:10:11.030 --> 00:10:13.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I said we needed
to go downstairs "fast,"</b></Default>

c0000254
00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:15.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I didn't mean to blow up
the whole freakin' floor.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:10:15.490 --> 00:10:17.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would this be me?</b></Default>

c0000256
00:10:17.160 --> 00:10:18.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm just bustin' your chops.</b></Default>

c0000257
00:10:19.240 --> 00:10:20.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm betting it was the Hydras.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:10:21.580 --> 00:10:23.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hang on, where'd she go?</b></Default>

c0000259
00:10:26.790 --> 00:10:28.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasp]</b></Default>

c0000260
00:10:28.500 --> 00:10:31.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Vichyssoise laughing]</b></Default>

c0000261
00:10:34.050 --> 00:10:37.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've done it!
Sisbell has been captured!</b></Default>

c0000262
00:10:37.550 --> 00:10:38.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What? No!</b></Default>

c0000263
00:10:39.060 --> 00:10:40.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm? Oh.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:10:40.640 --> 00:10:42.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire.
Soldiers, eh?</b></Default>

c0000265
00:10:43.100 --> 00:10:44.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALL]
Lady Sisbell, no!</b></Default>

c0000266
00:10:44.940 --> 00:10:45.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000267
00:10:47.520 --> 00:10:48.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Give her back!</b></Default>

c0000268
00:10:49.320 --> 00:10:50.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stop this!</b></Default>

c0000269
00:10:50.360 --> 00:10:52.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She is our nation's
greatest treasure, you fiend!</b></Default>

c0000270
00:10:53.280 --> 00:10:55.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got some bad news.</b></Default>

c0000271
00:10:55.110 --> 00:10:57.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your master's
never coming back.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:10:57.870 --> 00:10:59.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's ours!</b></Default>

c0000273
00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:02.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Shut up!
Release our lady, right now!</b></Default>

c0000274
00:11:02.250 --> 00:11:03.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Or die, you monster!</b></Default>

c0000275
00:11:03.960 --> 00:11:05.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You idiot.
Stand down!</b></Default>

c0000276
00:11:05.830 --> 00:11:07.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Witch! Give Lady Sisbell back!</b></Default>

c0000277
00:11:08.420 --> 00:11:10.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Right now!
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000278
00:11:13.300 --> 00:11:14.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Yumilecia grunts]</b></Default>

c0000279
00:11:14.720 --> 00:11:16.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000280
00:11:16.390 --> 00:11:18.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It hurts! Hm!</b></Default>

c0000281
00:11:18.600 --> 00:11:20.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nope! Just kidding!</b></Default>

c0000282
00:11:20.470 --> 00:11:21.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000283
00:11:22.470 --> 00:11:24.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[Yumilecia groaning]
-[sword clanking]</b></Default>

c0000284
00:11:24.350 --> 00:11:25.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000285
00:11:25.640 --> 00:11:27.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[VICHYSSOISE]
You have such a cute face.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:11:28.020 --> 00:11:30.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nothing but the best
for the Lou family.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:11:30.150 --> 00:11:31.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They sure know how to pick 'em.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:11:32.070 --> 00:11:33.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Such a shame.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:11:33.240 --> 00:11:34.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Makes me wanna crush you more.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:11:35.150 --> 00:11:36.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000291
00:11:36.240 --> 00:11:37.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No. Stop this!</b></Default>

c0000292
00:11:37.610 --> 00:11:40.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No way!
You can't make me!</b></Default>

c0000293
00:11:41.080 --> 00:11:42.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Hey! Vichyssoise!</b></Default>

c0000294
00:11:42.950 --> 00:11:44.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000295
00:11:45.790 --> 00:11:48.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Iska's here!
-Welcome back!</b></Default>

c0000296
00:11:48.080 --> 00:11:49.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're alive?
Impossible!</b></Default>

c0000297
00:11:50.340 --> 00:11:51.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you attacked me,</b></Default>

c0000298
00:11:51.840 --> 00:11:53.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I released Talisman's wave!</b></Default>

c0000299
00:11:54.010 --> 00:11:54.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000300
00:11:55.050 --> 00:11:57.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You may have saved yourself
back there, brave knight.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:11:57.930 --> 00:11:59.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you're a bit
too late, here!</b></Default>

c0000302
00:12:00.350 --> 00:12:02.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-[VICHYSSOISE] Saint Disciple.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:12:02.930 --> 00:12:03.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Laters!</b></Default>

c0000304
00:12:05.810 --> 00:12:07.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh! Lady Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000305
00:12:07.190 --> 00:12:09.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yumilecia! It's too late now!</b></Default>

c0000306
00:12:09.560 --> 00:12:11.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hands off, soldier boy!</b></Default>

c0000307
00:12:11.690 --> 00:12:13.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If a servant
can't protect her master,</b></Default>

c0000308
00:12:13.980 --> 00:12:15.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then what good is she?</b></Default>

c0000309
00:12:16.280 --> 00:12:18.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Don't worry, we'll save her.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000310
00:12:19.070 --> 00:12:21.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You go get everyone
outta here, then hide!</b></Default>

c0000311
00:12:21.870 --> 00:12:24.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts] And why should
we ever trust you?</b></Default>

c0000312
00:12:25.040 --> 00:12:26.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Sisbell was kidnapped</b></Default>

c0000313
00:12:26.580 --> 00:12:28.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>while you just stood
there, remember?</b></Default>

c0000314
00:12:28.170 --> 00:12:29.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gunshot]
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000315
00:12:29.370 --> 00:12:31.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tough talk from the girl
who was taken hostage.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:12:31.750 --> 00:12:33.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh.
-He saved you.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:12:33.800 --> 00:12:35.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why do you think Iska
called that thing's name</b></Default>

c0000318
00:12:35.880 --> 00:12:36.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to distract it?</b></Default>

c0000319
00:12:37.420 --> 00:12:38.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it hadn't been for him,</b></Default>

c0000320
00:12:39.470 --> 00:12:41.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your face would've
been crushed.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:12:42.010 --> 00:12:43.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm...
Hm.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:12:44.850 --> 00:12:46.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can trust me.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:12:46.100 --> 00:12:47.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll get Sisbell back.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:12:47.890 --> 00:12:48.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I promise.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:12:49.230 --> 00:12:50.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000326
00:12:52.020 --> 00:12:53.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I fail you,</b></Default>

c0000327
00:12:53.270 --> 00:12:55.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you have my permission
to kill me.</b></Default>

c0000328
00:12:55.230 --> 00:12:56.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000329
00:12:56.320 --> 00:12:57.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't go into detail.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:12:57.780 --> 00:12:59.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we came to the Sovereignty</b></Default>

c0000331
00:12:59.200 --> 00:13:00.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on a mission
to protect Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000332
00:13:00.950 --> 00:13:02.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if it cost us our lives.</b></Default>

c0000333
00:13:03.700 --> 00:13:05.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If you want to protect her,</b></Default>

c0000334
00:13:05.330 --> 00:13:07.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>trust me, and please do
as I say for now.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:13:08.040 --> 00:13:10.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:13:10.960 --> 00:13:12.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[rumbling]
-[all gasp]</b></Default>

c0000337
00:13:12.080 --> 00:13:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should leave now.
The palace is collapsing!</b></Default>

c0000338
00:13:14.210 --> 00:13:15.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Quick! Move out!
-[both gasp]</b></Default>

c0000339
00:13:16.460 --> 00:13:17.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Right!
-Right!</b></Default>

c0000340
00:13:17.590 --> 00:13:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You promise to do as I say,</b></Default>

c0000341
00:13:19.840 --> 00:13:21.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll let go of your hand
right now.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:13:21.640 --> 00:13:23.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[rumbling]</b></Default>

c0000343
00:13:24.050 --> 00:13:25.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[YUMILECIA]
Yeah, I promise.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:13:25.890 --> 00:13:26.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just tonight.</b></Default>

c0000345
00:13:28.930 --> 00:13:30.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If we get Lady Sisbell back,</b></Default>

c0000346
00:13:30.520 --> 00:13:32.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll agree to whatever deal
that I must.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:13:33.190 --> 00:13:34.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:13:34.980 --> 00:13:37.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shattering]</b></Default>

c0000349
00:13:38.990 --> 00:13:42.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000350
00:13:42.950 --> 00:13:45.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Rin, what's taking you so long?</b></Default>

c0000351
00:13:45.990 --> 00:13:48.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, I haven't heard
from you in a while.</b></Default>

c0000352
00:13:49.330 --> 00:13:50.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000353
00:13:51.330 --> 00:13:53.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin? I'm glad you're all right!</b></Default>

c0000354
00:13:54.080 --> 00:13:55.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are the wounded in safe hands?</b></Default>

c0000355
00:13:55.960 --> 00:13:58.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes! They're currently
receiving treatment</b></Default>

c0000356
00:13:58.130 --> 00:13:59.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>back at Lou's shelter.</b></Default>

c0000357
00:14:00.130 --> 00:14:01.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KISASAGE]
Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000358
00:14:01.180 --> 00:14:02.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tires screeching]</b></Default>

c0000359
00:14:02.840 --> 00:14:04.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A Saint Disciple,
in the Queen's Hall!</b></Default>

c0000360
00:14:05.180 --> 00:14:06.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're kidding me!</b></Default>

c0000361
00:14:06.970 --> 00:14:07.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-Hm.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:14:10.640 --> 00:14:13.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice, I know what you think.</b></Default>

c0000363
00:14:13.650 --> 00:14:15.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As long as you're there,
you can protect everything</b></Default>

c0000364
00:14:16.020 --> 00:14:17.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from falling apart.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:14:18.610 --> 00:14:21.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Repel their army,
and save the queen.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:14:22.070 --> 00:14:24.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your strong spirit
gives you that confidence.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:14:25.070 --> 00:14:27.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For all your people,
you have a benevolent soul.</b></Default>

c0000368
00:14:28.240 --> 00:14:30.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it means protecting
the Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000369
00:14:30.330 --> 00:14:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you have the ability
to suppress your emotions,</b></Default>

c0000370
00:14:33.000 --> 00:14:34.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>drown out your fears,</b></Default>

c0000371
00:14:34.630 --> 00:14:37.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>summon the strength to fight
mercilessly to the end.</b></Default>

c0000372
00:14:38.090 --> 00:14:40.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>These traits are wonderful
for a leader to have.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:14:41.590 --> 00:14:42.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But it won't do.</b></Default>

c0000374
00:14:43.550 --> 00:14:45.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your way only creates
a paradise</b></Default>

c0000375
00:14:45.340 --> 00:14:47.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for the strong to survive.</b></Default>

c0000376
00:14:48.720 --> 00:14:49.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your idealism,</b></Default>

c0000377
00:14:50.060 --> 00:14:52.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's a byproduct
of your undeniable strength.</b></Default>

c0000378
00:14:54.100 --> 00:14:57.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't save all astral mages
with narrow focus.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:14:58.320 --> 00:15:00.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Speaking for everyone
who wasn't blessed</b></Default>

c0000380
00:15:00.400 --> 00:15:02.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a strong astral spirit.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:15:03.110 --> 00:15:05.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall see that
this false paradise</b></Default>

c0000382
00:15:05.570 --> 00:15:07.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>burns to the ground.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:15:07.780 --> 00:15:09.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Etch this
into your memory, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:15:10.490 --> 00:15:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feel the despair.</b></Default>

c0000385
00:15:12.790 --> 00:15:13.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As I die,</b></Default>

c0000386
00:15:14.290 --> 00:15:16.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>slain by Imperials
you can't stop.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:15:18.170 --> 00:15:22.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000388
00:15:22.920 --> 00:15:24.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-What?</b></Default>

c0000389
00:15:24.470 --> 00:15:27.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[roaring]</b></Default>

c0000390
00:15:29.140 --> 00:15:30.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thuds]</b></Default>

c0000391
00:15:30.890 --> 00:15:32.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Grandfather!</b></Default>

c0000392
00:15:32.390 --> 00:15:34.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please let me deal
with these soldiers myself!</b></Default>

c0000393
00:15:35.890 --> 00:15:38.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the little girl's thorns
don't work on that thing,</b></Default>

c0000394
00:15:38.940 --> 00:15:41.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm guessing that
it's pure astral energy.</b></Default>

c0000395
00:15:41.360 --> 00:15:43.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which makes it invulnerable
to taking damage</b></Default>

c0000396
00:15:43.650 --> 00:15:45.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from my physical attacks.</b></Default>

c0000397
00:15:45.990 --> 00:15:48.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell me I'm right,
my nameless friend.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:15:49.410 --> 00:15:50.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
It's an avatar</b></Default>

c0000399
00:15:50.580 --> 00:15:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>created by a so-called
"spirit of sin."</b></Default>

c0000400
00:15:53.290 --> 00:15:55.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In short,
it's basically invincible.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:15:55.460 --> 00:15:58.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wh...? Aw, you lost
your left arm?</b></Default>

c0000402
00:15:58.330 --> 00:15:59.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
I'll get him next time.</b></Default>

c0000403
00:16:00.040 --> 00:16:03.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughing]</b></Default>

c0000404
00:16:03.380 --> 00:16:05.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, isn't that the sweetest?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:16:05.300 --> 00:16:08.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Gwandpa stepped in to save
his wittle gwandaughter.</b></Default>

c0000406
00:16:09.180 --> 00:16:11.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think I might actually cry!</b></Default>

c0000407
00:16:14.730 --> 00:16:17.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hate you beyond words.
Truly.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:16:18.650 --> 00:16:19.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000409
00:16:20.060 --> 00:16:22.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON] Kissing.
You must return at once.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:16:23.230 --> 00:16:24.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[KISSING]
Uncle On?</b></Default>

c0000411
00:16:25.440 --> 00:16:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
Something unexpected happened.</b></Default>

c0000412
00:16:27.820 --> 00:16:29.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm going to stop now
and head back as well.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:16:30.410 --> 00:16:31.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like what?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:16:31.910 --> 00:16:32.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
It's Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:16:33.240 --> 00:16:35.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's headed
to the Queen's Hall.</b></Default>

c0000416
00:16:35.700 --> 00:16:38.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What?
That's impossible.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:16:38.500 --> 00:16:41.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She useless in a fight,
her power's not for combat.</b></Default>

c0000418
00:16:41.670 --> 00:16:44.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why would she
choose now to leave?</b></Default>

c0000419
00:16:44.380 --> 00:16:45.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON]
Good question.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:16:45.670 --> 00:16:47.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a shelter
near her location.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:16:47.800 --> 00:16:49.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought she would
have gone there.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:16:49.720 --> 00:16:52.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[glass shattering]
-[Johaim groans]</b></Default>

c0000423
00:16:52.300 --> 00:16:53.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
This room was sundered</b></Default>

c0000424
00:16:53.640 --> 00:16:55.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>by an air scythe that can slice</b></Default>

c0000425
00:16:55.270 --> 00:16:57.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>the Imperial army's
bombers in half.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:16:58.520 --> 00:17:00.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could you possibly
survive that?</b></Default>

c0000427
00:17:01.860 --> 00:17:03.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's impressive.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:17:03.480 --> 00:17:04.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Great show of force.</b></Default>

c0000429
00:17:05.400 --> 00:17:07.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>An attack fit
for the descendants</b></Default>

c0000430
00:17:07.150 --> 00:17:08.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Founder.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:17:08.240 --> 00:17:09.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Anyone targets
your weak points,</b></Default>

c0000432
00:17:09.860 --> 00:17:12.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and it counters.
Useful, indeed!</b></Default>

c0000433
00:17:13.200 --> 00:17:15.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I asked how you survived,
and nothing more.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:17:17.250 --> 00:17:18.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's who I am.</b></Default>

c0000435
00:17:18.750 --> 00:17:20.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Next time, you're done.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:17:20.420 --> 00:17:22.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't appreciate the way
you grimace at me.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:17:23.250 --> 00:17:25.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In my wealth of experience,
looks can kill.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:17:26.550 --> 00:17:28.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So I want you gone.</b></Default>

c0000439
00:17:28.260 --> 00:17:30.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lost in the tempest of wind.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:17:30.720 --> 00:17:34.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Impact, God and World of Wind,
Mandala.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:17:34.510 --> 00:17:35.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind whooshing]</b></Default>

c0000442
00:17:35.930 --> 00:17:38.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You misjudged me,
as I thought you would.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:17:38.600 --> 00:17:39.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000444
00:17:39.890 --> 00:17:42.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your wind evades anything
with astral energy.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:17:43.190 --> 00:17:45.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is to avoid
hurting your own people.</b></Default>

c0000446
00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:46.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was your undoing.</b></Default>

c0000447
00:17:47.150 --> 00:17:48.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000448
00:17:48.320 --> 00:17:50.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] It was you.
You're the traitor?</b></Default>

c0000449
00:17:51.280 --> 00:17:52.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's right.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:17:52.410 --> 00:17:54.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I betrayed you
to change this nation.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:17:54.780 --> 00:17:57.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You wouldn't do it,
and someone had to.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:17:57.580 --> 00:17:59.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew who you really were.</b></Default>

c0000453
00:17:59.540 --> 00:18:01.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But you only saw me
as an enemy soldier</b></Default>

c0000454
00:18:01.500 --> 00:18:03.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because you were
blinded by power.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:18:03.790 --> 00:18:05.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's the difference!</b></Default>

c0000456
00:18:05.540 --> 00:18:06.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[sword clanging]
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000457
00:18:07.670 --> 00:18:08.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is it.</b></Default>

c0000458
00:18:09.130 --> 00:18:11.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our nation's turning point!</b></Default>

c0000459
00:18:11.430 --> 00:18:12.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000460
00:18:14.640 --> 00:18:15.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Elletear groaning]</b></Default>

c0000461
00:18:16.390 --> 00:18:18.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[Elletear gasping]</b></Default>

c0000462
00:18:19.730 --> 00:18:21.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[blood splashing]
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000463
00:18:23.270 --> 00:18:24.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[shuddered breathing]
Run.</b></Default>

c0000464
00:18:25.610 --> 00:18:27.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You have to escape, Mother.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:18:27.860 --> 00:18:29.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, you must leave.
[groans]</b></Default>

c0000466
00:18:30.820 --> 00:18:31.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[thuds]
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000467
00:18:34.200 --> 00:18:36.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
No. Elletear.</b></Default>

c0000468
00:18:43.080 --> 00:18:44.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's Elletear and Mother.</b></Default>

c0000469
00:18:46.170 --> 00:18:47.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What have you done to them?</b></Default>

c0000470
00:18:49.170 --> 00:18:50.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sword clanging]</b></Default>

c0000471
00:18:51.010 --> 00:18:53.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This nation has fallen.</b></Default>

c0000472
00:18:54.930 --> 00:18:55.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
It can't.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:18:58.810 --> 00:19:00.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Saint Disciple?</b></Default>

c0000474
00:19:00.720 --> 00:19:02.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, he doesn't matter.</b></Default>

c0000475
00:19:03.270 --> 00:19:04.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was too soft.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:19:05.730 --> 00:19:07.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm the reason
Mother and Elletear</b></Default>

c0000477
00:19:07.480 --> 00:19:08.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are bleeding out on the floor.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:19:09.860 --> 00:19:11.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I should have never
let my guard down.</b></Default>

c0000479
00:19:12.110 --> 00:19:13.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Imperials are meant to die.</b></Default>

c0000480
00:19:14.320 --> 00:19:15.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you like to join them?</b></Default>

c0000481
00:19:16.910 --> 00:19:19.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] You scoundrels
are all the same!</b></Default>

c0000482
00:19:20.580 --> 00:19:21.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That freezing air.</b></Default>

c0000483
00:19:22.080 --> 00:19:23.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Ice Calamity Witch.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:25.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Yes, that's right.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:19:25.870 --> 00:19:26.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A witch.</b></Default>

c0000486
00:19:27.630 --> 00:19:29.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Ice Calamity herself.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:19:29.290 --> 00:19:31.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your whole Empire will freeze.</b></Default>

c0000488
00:19:31.340 --> 00:19:32.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Including you!</b></Default>

c0000489
00:19:33.130 --> 00:19:34.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, stop!
Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000490
00:19:34.760 --> 00:19:35.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000491
00:19:35.840 --> 00:19:38.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JOHAIM]
You fail to grasp this reality.</b></Default>

c0000492
00:19:38.350 --> 00:19:40.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've captured a pureblood.</b></Default>

c0000493
00:19:40.140 --> 00:19:41.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now, I shall leave.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:19:41.640 --> 00:19:43.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Silence, you cur!</b></Default>

c0000495
00:19:43.560 --> 00:19:44.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This ends now!</b></Default>

c0000496
00:19:45.100 --> 00:19:46.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll never make it out
of here in one piece,</b></Default>

c0000497
00:19:47.020 --> 00:19:48.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so help me!</b></Default>

c0000498
00:19:48.860 --> 00:19:49.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that so?</b></Default>

c0000499
00:19:51.110 --> 00:19:52.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
You're running?</b></Default>

c0000500
00:19:52.860 --> 00:19:54.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There is a hidden passageway
in the back,</b></Default>

c0000501
00:19:55.280 --> 00:19:57.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but it'll never open
unless a descendant</b></Default>

c0000502
00:19:57.200 --> 00:19:58.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Founder touches it.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:19:58.780 --> 00:19:59.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I have a key.</b></Default>

c0000504
00:20:00.530 --> 00:20:01.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh!</b></Default>

c0000505
00:20:01.660 --> 00:20:05.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000506
00:20:05.660 --> 00:20:07.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[rumbling]
-[sword clinking]</b></Default>

c0000507
00:20:07.710 --> 00:20:08.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Scumbag!</b></Default>

c0000508
00:20:08.960 --> 00:20:11.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How dare you use my sister
like she's your tool!</b></Default>

c0000509
00:20:12.420 --> 00:20:14.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JOHAIM]
I'm putting her to good use.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:20:15.380 --> 00:20:17.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh! Mother!
[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000511
00:20:18.300 --> 00:20:19.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin, will she be all right?</b></Default>

c0000512
00:20:21.100 --> 00:20:23.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The laceration on her left arm
is down to the bone.</b></Default>

c0000513
00:20:25.060 --> 00:20:27.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She needs a surgical suture,
right away.</b></Default>

c0000514
00:20:27.440 --> 00:20:29.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000515
00:20:29.650 --> 00:20:31.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.
You take the lead on this.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:20:32.570 --> 00:20:34.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I trust you to do
what you think is best.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:20:34.900 --> 00:20:35.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:36.530 --> 00:20:37.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, ma'am.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:20:39.740 --> 00:20:40.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is he?</b></Default>

c0000520
00:20:40.950 --> 00:20:43.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000521
00:20:43.660 --> 00:20:45.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I won't let him get away
with my sister!</b></Default>

c0000522
00:20:47.080 --> 00:20:49.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh.
-[tires screeching]</b></Default>

c0000523
00:20:50.750 --> 00:20:52.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice, please get in!</b></Default>

c0000524
00:20:53.210 --> 00:20:54.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Warvick!</b></Default>

c0000525
00:20:54.710 --> 00:20:56.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can thank Miss Rin.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:20:56.470 --> 00:20:58.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She said you could use
a driver.</b></Default>

c0000527
00:20:58.510 --> 00:20:59.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's a lifesaver.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:21:00.220 --> 00:21:01.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Let's go, hit the gas!</b></Default>

c0000529
00:21:01.970 --> 00:21:03.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Right!
-[tires screeching]</b></Default>

c0000530
00:21:05.390 --> 00:21:07.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[tires screeching]
-[engine revving]</b></Default>

c0000531
00:21:10.190 --> 00:21:11.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Please hurry!</b></Default>

c0000532
00:21:11.310 --> 00:21:13.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elletear's wound
is life-threatening!</b></Default>

c0000533
00:21:14.190 --> 00:21:17.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm very aware of that,
but...then what?</b></Default>

c0000534
00:21:18.530 --> 00:21:20.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[engine revving]
-[tires screeching]</b></Default>

c0000535
00:21:21.110 --> 00:21:22.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Here's what we're going to do.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:21:22.740 --> 00:21:23.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We need to get that car</b></Default>

c0000537
00:21:23.950 --> 00:21:25.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and immediately head
to the hospital.</b></Default>

c0000538
00:21:26.160 --> 00:21:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, of course.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:21:28.290 --> 00:21:31.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] But...if it's too late
for Elletear,</b></Default>

c0000540
00:21:31.120 --> 00:21:33.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we need to head back
to the palace right away.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:21:34.920 --> 00:21:36.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WARVICK] Is it because you
want to get back to the queen?</b></Default>

c0000542
00:21:39.800 --> 00:21:40.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not quite.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:42.300 --> 00:21:44.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must crush the Imperial army.</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:46.220 --> 00:21:47.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:47.720 --> 00:21:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Understood.</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:48.930 --> 00:21:55.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000547
00:21:56.570 --> 00:21:59.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[tires screeching]</b></Default>

c0000548
00:22:00.820 --> 00:22:01.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gunshots]
-[WARVICK] Lady Alice,</b></Default>

c0000549
00:22:01.990 --> 00:22:03.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please hang on!</b></Default>

c0000550
00:22:03.820 --> 00:22:05.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ugh!
[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000551
00:22:05.410 --> 00:22:09.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000552
00:22:09.200 --> 00:22:10.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Drive Faster!
-Right!</b></Default>

c0000553
00:22:11.040 --> 00:22:13.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[engine revving]</b></Default>

c0000554
00:22:13.710 --> 00:22:15.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
No, stop!</b></Default>

c0000555
00:22:15.880 --> 00:22:18.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[tires screeching]
-[explosion]</b></Default>

c0000556
00:22:18.920 --> 00:22:21.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[glass shattering]</b></Default>

c0000557
00:22:21.220 --> 00:22:22.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Was this also a trap?</b></Default>

c0000558
00:22:24.050 --> 00:22:26.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He made it look like he was
carrying Elletear out.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:22:27.720 --> 00:22:30.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind howling]</b></Default>

c0000560
00:22:33.020 --> 00:22:34.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[WARVICK] [groans]
Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000561
00:22:35.480 --> 00:22:37.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]
Wake up, please.</b></Default>

c0000562
00:22:38.230 --> 00:22:40.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hm.
-My Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000563
00:22:41.400 --> 00:22:44.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000564
00:22:45.030 --> 00:22:46.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Warvick.</b></Default>

c0000565
00:22:46.450 --> 00:22:48.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Glad you're all right, ma'am.</b></Default>

c0000566
00:22:49.580 --> 00:22:50.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000567
00:22:51.160 --> 00:22:52.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000568
00:22:52.790 --> 00:22:55.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackles]</b></Default>

c0000569
00:22:56.130 --> 00:22:58.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Warvick, did...
Did you shield me?</b></Default>

c0000570
00:22:58.590 --> 00:23:01.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackles]</b></Default>

c0000571
00:23:02.300 --> 00:23:03.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll call and get you help!</b></Default>

c0000572
00:23:04.720 --> 00:23:07.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Rin!
Send a medical team, stat!</b></Default>

c0000573
00:23:07.800 --> 00:23:08.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like, now!</b></Default>

c0000574
00:23:09.350 --> 00:23:11.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Alice?
I'll send them right away!</b></Default>

c0000575
00:23:12.680 --> 00:23:13.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Counting on it.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:23:14.440 --> 00:23:15.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh.</b></Default>

c0000577
00:23:15.560 --> 00:23:18.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackles]</b></Default>

c0000578
00:23:21.070 --> 00:23:22.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpers]</b></Default>

c0000579
00:23:22.990 --> 00:23:24.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000580
00:23:26.070 --> 00:23:27.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's not fair!</b></Default>

c0000581
00:23:28.080 --> 00:23:30.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was supposed
to save everyone.</b></Default>

c0000582
00:23:32.370 --> 00:23:35.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But Mother, and Elletear.
[crying]</b></Default>

c0000583
00:23:36.460 --> 00:23:37.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And even Warvick.</b></Default>

c0000584
00:23:39.380 --> 00:23:42.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I failed.
[crying]</b></Default>

c0000585
00:23:43.920 --> 00:23:44.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's wrong.</b></Default>

c0000586
00:23:46.800 --> 00:23:49.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're all dying and nothing
is going my way!</b></Default>

c0000587
00:23:52.600 --> 00:23:54.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I put out the fires
in the palace,</b></Default>

c0000588
00:23:54.890 --> 00:23:56.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>raced to the Queen's Hall,</b></Default>

c0000589
00:23:56.600 --> 00:23:58.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>desperate to protect Mother.</b></Default>

c0000590
00:23:59.060 --> 00:24:00.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I chased down that murderer.</b></Default>

c0000591
00:24:01.360 --> 00:24:04.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hunted him all the way
here to get my sister back.</b></Default>

c0000592
00:24:04.440 --> 00:24:07.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackles]</b></Default>

c0000593
00:24:08.070 --> 00:24:09.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But I have failed.</b></Default>

c0000594
00:24:09.700 --> 00:24:10.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right at the end.</b></Default>

c0000595
00:24:12.740 --> 00:24:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[crying]</b></Default>

c0000596
00:24:17.830 --> 00:24:19.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In this critical moment,</b></Default>

c0000597
00:24:20.090 --> 00:24:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when they needed me most,</b></Default>

c0000598
00:24:21.960 --> 00:24:23.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I couldn't save</b></Default>

c0000599
00:24:23.340 --> 00:24:25.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>one single person.</b></Default>

c0000600
00:24:27.260 --> 00:24:28.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This army.</b></Default>

c0000601
00:24:28.930 --> 00:24:29.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

c0000602
00:24:30.180 --> 00:24:32.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every facet of the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000603
00:24:33.060 --> 00:24:34.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hear me now.</b></Default>

c0000604
00:24:34.560 --> 00:24:36.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If tearing me down
and destroying the people</b></Default>

c0000605
00:24:37.020 --> 00:24:38.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I love is your intention,</b></Default>

c0000606
00:24:38.650 --> 00:24:40.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then I will never forgive you!</b></Default>

c0000607
00:24:41.610 --> 00:24:42.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Prepare yourselves.</b></Default>

c0000608
00:24:43.480 --> 00:24:44.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're next.</b></Default>

c0000609
00:24:45.110 --> 00:24:47.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I won't fail
at getting my revenge.</b></Default>

c0000610
00:24:48.410 --> 00:24:49.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Alice!</b></Default>

c0000611
00:24:49.990 --> 00:24:50.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000612
00:24:51.410 --> 00:24:53.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[panting]</b></Default>

c0000613
00:24:53.990 --> 00:24:55.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're alive.</b></Default>

c0000614
00:24:55.120 --> 00:24:57.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[fire crackles]</b></Default>

c0000615
00:24:57.210 --> 00:24:58.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] [whimpering]
Iska.</b></Default>

